highlights.text: “The Glen - Levi Heron Edit” by Levi Heron has been on Viral Songs Sweden the longest, at 90 days straight.
KPop Demon Hunters Cast has the most spots on Viral Songs Sweden. “Golden” is the highest at #11.
“I Was Made For Loving You” by Tori Kelly and Ed Sheeran is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Sweden, up 19 spots at #60.
“Confess Your Love” by Jiandro and ola.wav is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Sweden at #16.
